ZH: 我是一名大学生，现在在一家公司做实习生。
EN: I am a college student and currently working as an intern in a company.

ZH: 这个公司每年都会招收很多实习生。
EN: This company recruits a large number of interns every year.

ZH: 作为一名实习生，我主要负责文件整理和资料收集。
EN: As an intern, I am mainly responsible for file sorting and data collection.

ZH: 经过几个月的实习，我学到了很多实践经验。
EN: After several months of internship, I have gained a lot of practical experience.

ZH: 实习生们每天都要按时打卡上班。
EN: Interns have to clock in on time every day.

ZH: 我的实习生期限是三个月。
EN: My internship period is three months.

ZH: 作为实习生，我需要带上自己的笔记本电脑。
EN: As an intern, I need to bring my own laptop.

ZH: 实习生们在完成任务时需要向导师汇报。
EN: Interns need to report to their supervisors when completing tasks.

ZH: 实习生们每周都会参加公司举办的培训课程。
EN: Interns participate in company training courses every week.

ZH: 这个实习机会对我的职业发展非常有帮助。
EN: This internship opportunity is very helpful for my career development.

ZH: 实习生们需要具备良好的沟通和团队合作能力。
EN: Interns need to have good communication and teamwork skills.

ZH: 公司为实习生提供了免费的午餐。
EN: The company provides free lunch for interns.

ZH: 实习生们必须遵守公司的规章制度。
EN: Interns must comply with the company's rules and regulations.

ZH: 实习生们应该积极主动地参与工作中的各种任务。
EN: Interns should actively participate in various tasks at work.

ZH: 实习期间，我有机会与各个部门的员工合作。
EN: During the internship, I have the opportunity to collaborate with employees from different departments.

ZH: 实习结束后，公司会给予实习生一份工作证明。
EN: After the internship ends, the company will provide interns with a certificate of completion.

ZH: 实习生们经常需要完成一些简单的办公室职责。
EN: Interns often need to complete some simple office duties.

ZH: 我喜欢这个实习生岗位，因为可以学到很多新知识。
EN: I enjoy this internship position because I can learn a lot of new knowledge.

ZH: 实习生们在工作过程中可以提出建议和改进方法。
EN: Interns can propose suggestions and improvement methods during the work process.

ZH: 实习期间，我会积极努力地展现自己的能力和潜力。
EN: During the internship, I will actively demonstrate my abilities and potential.
